1. show more message
set cmdheight=2
then when press key, the binding function will show on mini buffer

2. interactive
let g:ot = 0
function! SimpleComplete()
    execute 'echo '.g:ot
endfunction
then when this function is called, will echo message on mini buffer

3. purge plugin installed by tarball
 Download supertab.vmb to any directory.
 Open the file in vim ($ vim supertab.vmb).
 Source the file (:so %).

 uninstall supertab
 rm .vim/plugin/supertab.vim
 sudo rm /usr/share/vim/vimfiles/plugin/supertab.vim
 
 sudo find / -iname "supertab*"

